## 2. Code-Simplifier Plugin

Simplifies and refines code for clarity, consistency, and maintainability while preserving functionality.

### Verify Installation

Check for: `.cursor/plugins/code-simplifier/agents/code-simplifier.md`

### Install for New Project

Create the directory structure and agent file:

```bash
mkdir -p .cursor/plugins/code-simplifier/agents
```

Then create `.cursor/plugins/code-simplifier/agents/code-simplifier.md` with the standard agent definition (copy from an existing project like leonnes-prod).

### Agent File Contents

The code-simplifier.md should contain:
- YAML frontmatter with `name: code-simplifier`, `model: opus`
- Instructions to preserve functionality while simplifying
- Project-specific coding standards from CLAUDE.md
- Focus on recently modified code

