## 3. Superpowers Plugin (Claude Code CLI)

Provides structured workflows for TDD, systematic debugging, and collaborative planning.

### Verify Installation

In Claude Code CLI, check available commands:
```
/superpowers:brainstorm
/superpowers:write-plan
/superpowers:execute-plan
/superpowers:tdd
/superpowers:debug
```

### Install (in Claude Code CLI)

```bash
/plugin marketplace add obra/superpowers-marketplace
/plugin install superpowers@superpowers-marketplace
```

### Document in CLAUDE.md

Each project's CLAUDE.md should have an "AI Development Tooling" section documenting all 3 plugins with:
- Installation instructions
- Key commands/capabilities
- When to use each plugin

