## New Project Setup Procedure

When starting a new project:

1. **Create `.cursor/rules/` directory**
2. **Initialize claude-mem context:**
   ```bash
   mkdir -p .cursor/rules
   # Context will auto-populate on first session
   ```

3. **Add code-simplifier plugin:**
   ```bash
   mkdir -p .cursor/plugins/code-simplifier/agents
   # Copy code-simplifier.md from template project
   ```

4. **Update CLAUDE.md** with AI Development Tooling section including all 3 plugins

5. **Verify claude-mem worker** is running globally

